                            <title ref="LIT5888AsmatPrayer">Prayer for undoing charms, maftǝḥe śǝrāy</title>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ሸድኤል፡ ሸድፙኤል፡ ሄኤሁ፡</incipit>
